Definition: angered at something unjust or wrong
Example: an indignant denial; incensed at the judges' unfairness; a look of outraged disbelief; umbrageous at the loss of their territory
Synonyms: incensed, outraged, umbrageous, noun, feeling, umbrage, angered, at, something, unjust, or, wrong, an, denial, the, judges, unfairness, a, look, of, disbelief, loss, their, territory
Category: adj.all
